"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-ireland-2024-0723-1461260-county-olympic-couture\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Philip Bromwell  Two hundred and six countries will be represented by athletes at the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics, but amid the flags, fanfare and fireworks on Friday, you might spot a fashionable nod to 31 of the 32 counties of Ireland.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999840711099, \"rank\": 1.592693723355987e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The designer of Team Ireland's official uniform, Laura Weber, has included an embroidered county crest in each of the white jackets which will be worn by athletes as they sail down the Seine.\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999986853254, \"rank\": 1.2592071818798508e-09, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Weber_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Weber\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Weber_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Weber_White\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999942581326, \"rank\": 4.1974431726132635e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dubliner, who is based in New York, redesigned the traditional county crests with a new symbolism and a refreshed colour palette.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Dubliner_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.9999983408320199, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Dubliner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Dubliner_(magazine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Dubliner_(magazine)\"}, {\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999606907303, \"rank\": 3.722037042830954e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"All the athletes chose their county and the crest has been embroidered and placed on the jacket sleeve.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not only is this an amazing talking point for all the athletes, but it felt like a special tribute to all their families, their communities, their villages that have supported them just to get to the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The county crests - Leitrim aside, in case you are wondering - are one of a number of unique elements in the opening ceremony jackets.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They include four shamrocks representing the four provinces of Ireland and a four leaf shamrock embellished brooch.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999840711099, \"rank\": 1.592693723355987e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also a small opera pocket in the front of the jackets, referencing the suiting worn by Ireland's first Olympic athletes of 1924.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999840711099, \"rank\": 1.592693723355987e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Handily, for what promises to be a spectacular occasion for photographs and video, this now fits a mobile phone.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Several of the world's top fashion designers are supporting their country's Olympians by designing their team kit and ceremonial outfits, with Stella McCartney (Great Britain) and Giorgio Armani (Italy) two of the most prominent.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_McCartney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella McCartney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q3501317\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_McCartney\"}, {\"begin\": 1576, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9818321866578856, \"rank\": 0.01268677217007228, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgio_Armani\", \"score\": 0.9999999093454376, \"rank\": 9.065456125228487e-08, \"text\": \"Giorgio Armani\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgio_Armani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgio_Armani\"}, {\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9999885679288576, \"rank\": 8.562881499065646e-06, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mongolia's opening and closing ceremony outfits for Paris went viral after they were released, with many people saying how much they liked the traditional designs.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9973267045281518, \"rank\": 0.0026730477828841408, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.063422522419647e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Weber, whose company LW Pearl specialises in couture embellishment, is probably best known in Ireland for her embroidery for Jill Biden's coat and dress for her husband's inauguration in 2021.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"score\": 0.7570633205646543, \"rank\": 0.3143685445009013, \"text\": \"Weber\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\"}, {\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999840711099, \"rank\": 1.592693723355987e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jill Biden\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has worked with names like Rhianna, Kaia Gerber and Lily Aldridge and also with designers like Marc Jacobs, Proenza Schouler and Thom Browne among others.\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhianna_Pratchett\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 3.7638813020291935e-12, \"text\": \"Rhianna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhianna_Pratchett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhianna_Pratchett\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaia_Gerber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaia Gerber\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaia_Gerber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaia_Gerber\"}, {\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lily_Aldridge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lily Aldridge\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lily_Aldridge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lily_Aldridge\"}, {\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marc_Jacobs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marc Jacobs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q3501317\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marc_Jacobs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marc_Jacobs\"}, {\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Proenza_Schouler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Proenza Schouler\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Proenza_Schouler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Proenza_Schouler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, seeing Team Ireland at the opening ceremony will be a dream come true.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2184, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999986853254, \"rank\": 1.2592071818798508e-09, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have definitely dreamt of projects and collaborations like this.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This one is particularly special and the most special part is that I got to meet all these amazing athletes.\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are people who will inspire me for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only their discipline, hard work and dedication, but just their kindness and temperament.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has just been an absolute privilege to get to meet these athletes,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2706, \"end\": 